translate portuguese mcgee18_d2594747:

    # "Afterwards, we lie in bed for a moment, catching our breath."
    "Depois, ficamos deitados na cama por um momento, a recuperar o fôlego."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:18
translate portuguese mcgee18_f4e1b073:

    # mrmg "So, [pcname]..."
    mrmg "Então, [pcname]..."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:19
translate portuguese mcgee18_f6b60d54:

    # mrmg "Edie was saying that you're about to graduate. Any plans for after you finish school?"
    mrmg "A Edie disse que estás prestes a terminar o curso. Tens planos para depois de terminares a escola?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:20
translate portuguese mcgee18_158b58fb:

    # pc "Oh um... I'm not sure."
    pc "Oh, hum... Não tenho a certeza."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:23
translate portuguese mcgee18_338c53f3:

    # et "You're a smart boy. I hope you have some idea of what you're going to do."
    et "És um rapaz inteligente. Espero que tenhas alguma ideia do que vais fazer."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:24
translate portuguese mcgee18_a8107df4:

    # mrmg "Yeah, it's good to have a plan. Even if you don't end up sticking to it."
    mrmg "Sim, é bom ter um plano. Mesmo que acabes por não o seguir."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:25
translate portuguese mcgee18_67ffd2ed:

    # mrmg "When I was your age, I never would have imagined I'd be running a coffee shop in a small town."
    mrmg "Quando tinha a tua idade, nunca teria imaginado que estaria a gerir um café numa cidade pequena."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:26
translate portuguese mcgee18_6ed16a5b:

    # et "He wanted to be an architect."
    et "Ele queria ser arquiteto."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:27
translate portuguese mcgee18_1f4c7425:

    # mrmg "I couldn't ever wrap my head around the math."
    mrmg "Nunca consegui entender a matemática."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:30
translate portuguese mcgee18_7dc88a4e:

    # pc "I haven't decided exactly, but I may work in a lab somewhere, like my dad did. Or maybe travel?"
    pc "Ainda não decidi exatamente, mas talvez venha a trabalhar num laboratório algures, como o meu pai fez. Ou talvez viajar?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:31
translate portuguese mcgee18_a852eda0:

    # mrmg "Well you still have time. As long as you're moving forward, you know?"
    mrmg "Bem, ainda tens tempo. Desde que estejas a avançar, percebes?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:32
translate portuguese mcgee18_81828f00:

    # et "What about romance?"
    et "E quanto ao amor?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:33
translate portuguese mcgee18_f31c9253:

    # mrmg "Yes, any chance of you settling down soon?"
    mrmg "Sim, há alguma hipótese de te assentares em breve?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:38
translate portuguese mcgee18_0da9fddf:

    # pc "I have somebody in mind who I might want to settle down with, yeah."
    pc "Tenho alguém em mente com quem talvez queira assentar, sim."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:39
translate portuguese mcgee18_91054e3c:

    # et "That's great."
    et "Isso é ótimo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:40
translate portuguese mcgee18_039a1f3c:

    # mrmg "Yeah, we're happy for you!"
    mrmg "Sim, estamos felizes por ti!"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:42
translate portuguese mcgee18_3a5905ee:

    # pc "I haven't met anybody yet that I'd want to settle down with."
    pc "Ainda não conheci ninguém com quem queira assentar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:43
translate portuguese mcgee18_560976b8:

    # et "I'm sure you will. A young girl would be very lucky to be with you."
    et "Tenho a certeza de que vais conhecer. Uma rapariga teria muita sorte em estar contigo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:44
translate portuguese mcgee18_5a3cddaa:

    # mrmg "For sure. You'll get your pick of the litter and eventually find someone who checks all the boxes you're looking for."
    mrmg "Com certeza. Vais poder escolher a melhor e, eventualmente, encontrar alguém que preencha todos os requisitos que procuras."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:46
translate portuguese mcgee18_313c0671:

    # pc "Why settle, when I can mess around with a bunch of different people?"
    pc "Porquê assentar, quando posso divertir-me com um monte de pessoas diferentes?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:47
translate portuguese mcgee18_a1c5c517:

    # mrmg "Haha, it's true, that's fun... for a while."
    mrmg "Haha, é verdade, isso é divertido... por um tempo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:48
translate portuguese mcgee18_1e788beb:

    # et "I think that, eventually, you're going to want more though."
    et "Acho que, eventualmente, vais querer mais, no entanto."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:51
translate portuguese mcgee18_650ed17b:

    # mrmg "Edie and I were just talking about you the other night. About how we hope that you'll find a nice girl to marry."
    mrmg "A Edie e eu estávamos mesmo a falar de ti na outra noite. Sobre como esperamos que encontres uma rapariga simpática para casar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:52
translate portuguese mcgee18_39aeeae4:

    # et "Like we found each other."
    et "Tal como nós nos encontrámos."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:53
translate portuguese mcgee18_1c927abb:

    # mrmg "There's nothing quite like being in love with your best friend."
    mrmg "Não há nada como estar apaixonado pelo teu melhor amigo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:56
translate portuguese mcgee18_f53975a4:

    # pc "It does seem nice."
    pc "Parece mesmo bom."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:59
translate portuguese mcgee18_35c5f2a1:

    # "We get dressed and say our goodbyes."
    "Vestimo-nos e despedimo-nos."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:60
translate portuguese mcgee18_aea74b6e:

    # "Their relationship is a little strange, but damn they do love each other."
    "A relação deles é um pouco estranha, mas caramba, eles amam-se mesmo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:61
translate portuguese mcgee18_70b92f51:

    # "It must be nice to feel that close to another person. Maybe I will have something like that one day."
    "Deve ser bom sentir-se tão próximo de outra pessoa. Talvez um dia eu tenha algo assim."

